l_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) the Finan=
cial Times, as a way to =E2=80=9Ctransform the visual infinity that is in m=
y
mirror paintings.=E2=80=9D

* Stephanie Shih at Alexander Berggruen: After my visit to L=C3=A9vy Gorvy =
Dayan, I walked up Madison Avenue to Alexander Berggruen gallery, where Ale=
x Berggruen=E2=80=94the third generation of his family to deal art=E2=80=94=
has a solo presentation of ceramics by the young Taiwanese-American artist =
Stephanie Shih. The works are nostalgic depictions of classic 1990s foodstu=
ffs, consumer products, and cultural staples, like Hot Pockets, Solo laundr=
y
detergent, and an Alanis Morissette CD, all rendered in exquisite detail in=
