The show, titled Domestic Bliss, speaks to a certain middle-class suburban =
lifestyle riddled with unease and malaise. Her work Nuclear Family is a cer=
amic microwave with Stouffer=E2=80=99s and Kid Cuisine boxes on top and a H=
ungry-Man meal spinning inside. The VHS set Buns of Steel and box of Viagra=
